AudioVisualizer AudiVis 0.1
----------------------------

About
-----
AudiVis convert mp4 video footage on the basis of its audio.
Change the current mp4 file under ch.fhnw.meco.util.Constants.VIDEO_NAME.

Start
-----
Before you lanch the application under ch.fhnw.meco.ui.Launcher you need the following setup:
• VM-Options:     -Xmx1g -XX:MaxHeapSize=1g
• JDK:            1.8  32-bit (64-bit won't work due to Xuggler)
• Maven:          Run the Maven pom.xml (for installing Xuggler and co libs)

Frameworks
----------
• JDK 1.8
• Minim 2.2.0
• Xuggler 5.4

